<milestone unit="sentence" n="31" /> --Parties having negroes hired at <orgName type="division" n="Division 5">Fifth Division</orgName>, <placeName reg="Chimborazo Hospital">Chimborazo Hospital</placeName>, will call immediately and get their pay. They must come in person, as no orders for payment will be received. </p> <closer> <signed><persName n="Gaines,,H.,B.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00016" reg="default:Gaines,H.,B.,," authname="gaines,h.,b."><foreName full="yes">H.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">B.</foreName>  <surname full="yes">Gaines</surname></persName>,</signed> <lb /> <rs type="role">Steward</rs> of <orgName type="division" n="Division 5">Fifth Division</orgName>, <lb /> <placeName reg="Chimborazo Hospital">Chimborazo Hospital</placeName>. <term type="printrun">se 22--3t*</term> </closer> </div3> </div2> 
