<milestone unit="sentence" n="33" /> At <orgName n="Sycamore Church" type="church">Sycamore Church</orgName>, <placeName reg="Richmond, Richmond, Virginia" key="tgn,7013964" authname="tgn,7013964">Richmond, Virginia</placeName>, by <persName n="Pettigrew,Reverend,William,J.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00017" reg="default:Pettigrew,William,J.,," authname="pettigrew,william,j."><roleName n="Reverend" full="yes">Rev.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">William</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Pettigrew</surname></persName>, on the <dateStruct value="1864-09-21" full="yes" authname="1864-09-21"><day reg="21" full="yes">21st</day> of <month reg="09" full="yes">September</month>, <year full="yes">1864</year>,</dateStruct> <persName n="Woodson,Doctor,Landon,A.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00018" reg="default:Woodson,Landon,A.,," authname="woodson,landon,a."><roleName n="Doctor" full="yes">Dr.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Landon</foreName> <foreName full="yes">A.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Woodson</surname></persName>, <placeName reg="United States" key="tgn,7012149" authname="tgn,7012149">Confederate States</placeName> Army, to <persName n="Pearce,Miss,Sue,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00019" reg="default:Pearce,Sue,,," authname="pearce,sue"><roleName n="Miss" full="yes">Miss</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Sue</foreName> <surname full="yes">Pearce</surname></persName>, daughter of <persName n="Pearce,,John,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00020" reg="default:Pearce,John,,," authname="pearce,john"><foreName full="yes">John</foreName> <surname full="yes">Pearce</surname></persName>, <rs type="role">Esq.</rs> </p> </div4> </div3> 
<div3 type="death" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head>Died,</head> 
<div4 type="obit" n="1" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="34" /> On <dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Wednesday</day></dateStruct> <time>night</time>, the <dateStruct value="--22" full="yes" authname="---22"><day reg="22" full="yes">22d instant</day></dateStruct>, at <time value="2oclock">2 o'clock</time>, <persName n="Goode,,George,W.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00021" reg="default:Goode,George,W.,," authname="goode,george,w."><foreName full="yes">George</foreName> <foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Goode</surname></persName>, <num value="2" type="ordinal">second</num> son of <persName><foreName full="yes">William</foreName></persName> and <persName n="Goode,,Mildred,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00022" reg="default:Goode,Mildred,,," authname="goode,mildred"><foreName full="yes">Mildred</foreName> <surname full="yes">Goode</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="4years" type="date">four years</measure> and <measure n="6months" type="date">six months</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="35" /> The friends and acquaintances are respectfully invited to attend his funeral this (<dateStruct full="yes"><day type="name" full="yes">Friday</day></dateStruct>) Afternoon at <time value="3oclock">3 o'clock</time>, on <address><street n="2 Street">Second street</street></address>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="36" /> Killed, yesterday morning, by the enemy's shelling, near <placeName reg="Petersburg, Petersburg, Virginia" key="tgn,7014404" authname="tgn,7014404">Petersburg</placeName>, <persName n="Jarvis,,Ottaway,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00023" reg="default:Jarvis,Ottaway,,," authname="jarvis,ottaway"><foreName full="yes">Ottaway</foreName> <surname full="yes">Jarvis</surname></persName>, <num value="1" type="ordinal">First</num> Corporal in the <orgName n="Richmond Fayette Artillery" type="artillery">Richmond Fayette Artillery</orgName>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="37" /> The friends and acquaintances of the deceased, as well as those of <persName n="Jarvis,Mrs.,Frances,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00024" reg="default:Jarvis,Frances,,," authname="jarvis,frances"><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes">Mrs.</roleName> <foreName full="yes">Frances</foreName> <surname full="yes">Jarvis</surname></persName> and <persName n="Burwell,Mrs.,,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00025" reg="mostcommon:Burwell,nomatch:0" authname="burwell"><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes" /><surname full="yes">Burwell</surname></persName> and <persName n="Jones,Mrs.,Octavia,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00026" reg="default:Jones,Octavia,,," authname="jones,octavia"><roleName n="Mrs." full="yes" /><foreName full="yes">Octavia</foreName> <surname full="yes">Jones</surname></persName>, are respectfully invited to attend his funeral at <orgName n="Sycamore Church" type="church">Sycamore Church</orgName> to-day at <time value="11oclock">11 o'clock</time>. * </p> </div4> 
<div4 type="obit" n="2" org="uniform" sample="complete"> 
<head /> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="38" /> On <dateStruct value="-09-22" full="yes" authname="--09-22"><day type="name" full="yes">Thursday</day>, <day reg="22" full="yes">22d</day> <month reg="09" full="yes">September</month></dateStruct>, <persName n="Frances,,Mary,,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00027" reg="default:Frances,Mary,,," authname="frances,mary"><foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName> <surname full="yes">Frances</surname></persName>, only child of <persName><foreName full="yes">Mary</foreName></persName> and <persName n="Burke,,W.,J.,," id="n-0001.0000.00000.00028" reg="default:Burke,W.,J.,," authname="burke,w.,j."><foreName full="yes">W.</foreName> <foreName full="yes">J.</foreName> <surname full="yes">Burke</surname></persName>, aged <measure n="11months" type="date">eleven months</measure> and <measure n="4days" type="date">four days</measure>. </p> 
<p>

<milestone unit="sentence" n="39" /> Her funeral will take place this Afternoon at <time value="2:30oclock">half-past 2 o'clock</time>, from the residence of her parents, on <num value="10" type="ordinal">Tenth</num>, between <address><street n="Byrd street">Byrd</street></address> and <address><street n="Canal street">Canal streets</street></address>. * </p> </div4> </div3> </div2> 
